Toyo Trust Banking Co Ltd issue 100 mln dlr convertible eurobond due March 31 2002 pay indicate pct price par lead manager Toyo Trust International said. The issue callable 104 pct decline 1/2 pct annum par thereafter. It callable unless share price exceeds conversion price 150 pct. The sell concession 1-1/2 pct management underwriting pay 1/2 pct. Final term fix April 10. The payment date April 30 short coupon period. The issue list Luxembourg. REUTER 